{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":581,"text":"I'd like to talk to you today"},{"time":2851,"text":"about a whole new way to think\nabout sexual activity"},{"time":7037,"text":"and sexuality education, by comparison."},{"time":11110,"text":"If you talk to someone today in America"},{"time":13776,"text":"about sexual activity,"},{"time":15600,"text":"you'll find pretty soon\nyou're not just talking"},{"time":19248,"text":"about sexual activity."},{"time":20906,"text":"You're also talking about baseball."},{"time":23952,"text":"Because baseball is the dominant\ncultural metaphor"},{"time":28186,"text":"that Americans use to think about"},{"time":30704,"text":"and talk about sexual activity,"},{"time":33553,"text":"and we know that because there's"},{"time":35101,"text":"all this language in English"},{"time":37685,"text":"that seems to be talking about baseball"},{"time":40630,"text":"but that's really talking\nabout sexual activity."},{"time":44489,"text":"So, for example, you can\nbe a pitcher or a catcher,"},{"time":47688,"text":"and that corresponds to whether you"},{"time":49615,"text":"perform a sexual act\nor receive a sexual act."},{"time":53383,"text":"Of course, there are the bases,"},{"time":54389,"text":"which refer to specific sexual activities"},{"time":57607,"text":"that happen in a very specific order,"},{"time":60822,"text":"ultimately resulting in scoring a run"},{"time":63600,"text":"or hitting a home run,"},{"time":64604,"text":"which is usually having\nvaginal intercourse"},{"time":66912,"text":"to the point of orgasm,"},{"time":68624,"text":"at least for the guy."},{"time":71017,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":72946,"text":"You can strike out, which means"},{"time":74447,"text":"you don't get to have any sexual activity."},{"time":76932,"text":"And if you're a benchwarmer,"},{"time":78290,"text":"you might be a virgin or somebody who for"},{"time":80705,"text":"whatever reason isn't in the game,"},{"time":82954,"text":"maybe because of your age\nor because of your ability"},{"time":86119,"text":"or because of your skillset."},{"time":89165,"text":"A bat's a penis,"},{"time":90783,"text":"and a nappy dugout\nis a vulva, or a vagina."},{"time":94852,"text":"A glove or a catcher's mitt is a condom."},{"time":97960,"text":"A switch-hitter is a bisexual person,"},{"time":100877,"text":"and we gay and lesbian folks\nplay for the other team."},{"time":104569,"text":"And then there's this one:"},{"time":107168,"text":"\"if there's grass\non the field, play ball.\""},{"time":111192,"text":"And that usually refers to"},{"time":113596,"text":"if a young person, specifically\noften a young woman,"},{"time":116953,"text":"is old enough to have pubic hair,"},{"time":118685,"text":"she's old enough to have sex with."},{"time":121410,"text":"This baseball model\nis incredibly problematic."},{"time":124393,"text":"It's sexist. It's heterosexist."},{"time":126744,"text":"It's competitive. It's goal-directed."},{"time":129120,"text":"And it can't result in healthy sexuality"},{"time":131903,"text":"developing in young people or in adults."},{"time":134951,"text":"So we need a new model."},{"time":136673,"text":"I'm here today to offer\nyou that new model."},{"time":139232,"text":"And it's based on"},{"time":141007,"text":"pizza."},{"time":142833,"text":"Now pizza is something\nthat is universally understood"},{"time":146280,"text":"and that most people associate\nwith a positive experience."},{"time":149177,"text":"So let's do this."},{"time":150157,"text":"Let's take baseball\nand pizza and compare it"},{"time":153126,"text":"when talking about three aspects\nof sexual activity:"},{"time":156570,"text":"the trigger for sexual activity,"},{"time":158223,"text":"what happens during sexual activity,"},{"time":160441,"text":"and the expected outcome\nof sexual activity."},{"time":163593,"text":"So when do you play baseball?"},{"time":166401,"text":"You play baseball when\nit's baseball season"},{"time":168841,"text":"and when there's a game on the schedule."},{"time":171123,"text":"It's not exactly your choice."},{"time":173433,"text":"So if it's prom night or a wedding night"},{"time":176329,"text":"or at a party or if our parents\naren't home,"},{"time":179399,"text":"hey, it's just batter up."},{"time":182131,"text":"Can you imagine saying to your coach,"},{"time":183917,"text":"\"Uh, I'm not really feeling it today,"},{"time":186418,"text":"I think I'll sit this game out.\""},{"time":188485,"text":"That's just not the way it happens."},{"time":190577,"text":"And when you get together\nto play baseball,"},{"time":192649,"text":"immediately you're\nwith two opposing teams,"},{"time":195100,"text":"one playing offense, one playing defense,"},{"time":197430,"text":"somebody's trying to move\ndeeper into the field."},{"time":200225,"text":"That's usually a sign to the boy."},{"time":202158,"text":"Somebody's trying to defend\npeople moving into the field."},{"time":205194,"text":"That's often given to the girl."},{"time":207423,"text":"It's competitive."},{"time":208458,"text":"We're not playing with each other."},{"time":210247,"text":"We're playing against each other."},{"time":211654,"text":"And when you show up to play baseball,"},{"time":213586,"text":"nobody needs to talk\nabout what we're going to do"},{"time":216130,"text":"or how this baseball game\nmight be good for us."},{"time":218671,"text":"Everybody knows the rules."},{"time":219934,"text":"You just take your position\nand play the game."},{"time":224313,"text":"But when do you have pizza?"},{"time":226673,"text":"Well, you have pizza when\nyou're hungry for pizza."},{"time":230915,"text":"It starts with an internal sense,\nan internal desire, or a need."},{"time":235009,"text":"\"Huh. I could go for some pizza.\""},{"time":238681,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":240938,"text":"And because it's an internal desire,"},{"time":243915,"text":"we actually have some sense\nof control over that."},{"time":246273,"text":"I could decide that I'm hungry"},{"time":247827,"text":"but know that it's not\na great time to eat."},{"time":251358,"text":"And then when we get together\nwith someone for pizza,"},{"time":254020,"text":"we're not competing with them,"},{"time":256870,"text":"we're looking for an experience"},{"time":258370,"text":"that both of us will share"},{"time":259656,"text":"that's satisfying for both of us,"},{"time":261630,"text":"and when you get together\nfor pizza with somebody,"},{"time":264635,"text":"what's the first thing you do?"},{"time":266183,"text":"You talk about it."},{"time":268105,"text":"You talk about what you want."},{"time":269636,"text":"You talk about what you like."},{"time":271129,"text":"You may even negotiate it."},{"time":272685,"text":"\"How do you feel\nabout pepperoni?\" (Laughter)"},{"time":275454,"text":"\"Not so much, I'm kind\nof a mushroom guy myself.\""},{"time":278081,"text":"\"Well, maybe we can go half and half.\""},{"time":280147,"text":"And even if you've had pizza with somebody"},{"time":282171,"text":"for a very long time,"},{"time":285206,"text":"don't you still say things like,"},{"time":287268,"text":"\"Should we get the usual?\""},{"time":289261,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":290424,"text":"\"Or maybe something\na little more adventurous?\""},{"time":294181,"text":"Okay, so when you're playing baseball,"},{"time":296015,"text":"so if we talk\nabout during sexual activity,"},{"time":298133,"text":"when you're playing baseball,"},{"time":299538,"text":"you're just supposed to round the bases"},{"time":302066,"text":"in the proper order one at a time."},{"time":304546,"text":"You can't hit the ball\nand run to right field."},{"time":306761,"text":"That doesn't work."},{"time":307983,"text":"And you also can't get\nto second base and say,"},{"time":310301,"text":"\"I like it here. I'm going to stay here.\""},{"time":314701,"text":"No."},{"time":316122,"text":"And also, of course,\nwith baseball, there's, like,"},{"time":318527,"text":"the specific equipment\nand a specific skill set."},{"time":321027,"text":"Not everybody can play baseball.\nIt's pretty exclusive."},{"time":324654,"text":"Okay, but what about pizza?"},{"time":326312,"text":"When we're trying to figure\nout what's good for pizza,"},{"time":328908,"text":"isn't it all about what's our pleasure?"},{"time":331593,"text":"There are a million different\nkinds of pizza."},{"time":333325,"text":"There's a million different toppings."},{"time":335111,"text":"There's a million different\nways to eat pizza."},{"time":337413,"text":"And none of them are wrong.\nThey're different."},{"time":340362,"text":"And in this case, difference is good,"},{"time":342810,"text":"because that's going\nto increase the chance"},{"time":344882,"text":"that we're having a satisfying experience."},{"time":347466,"text":"And lastly, what's the expected\noutcome of baseball?"},{"time":350426,"text":"Well, in baseball, you play to win."},{"time":354124,"text":"You score as many runs as you can."},{"time":356657,"text":"There's always a winner in baseball,"},{"time":358645,"text":"and that means there's always\na loser in baseball."},{"time":362066,"text":"But what about pizza?"},{"time":363722,"text":"Well, in pizza, we're not really --"},{"time":365933,"text":"there's no winning. How do you win pizza?"},{"time":369600,"text":"You don't. But you do look for,"},{"time":372855,"text":"\"Are we satisfied?\""},{"time":374576,"text":"And sometimes that can\nbe different amounts"},{"time":376648,"text":"over different times\nor with different people"},{"time":378815,"text":"or on different days."},{"time":380732,"text":"And we get to decide\nwhen we feel satisfied."},{"time":383862,"text":"If we're still hungry,\nwe might have some more."},{"time":386700,"text":"If you eat too much, though,"},{"time":388238,"text":"you just feel gross."},{"time":390143,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":392552,"text":"So what if we could take this pizza model"},{"time":395238,"text":"and overlay it on top\nof sexuality education?"},{"time":398610,"text":"A lot of sexuality education\nthat happens today"},{"time":401149,"text":"is so influenced by the baseball model,"},{"time":404575,"text":"and it sets up education that can't help"},{"time":408368,"text":"but produce unhealthy\nsexuality in young people."},{"time":412101,"text":"And those young people\nbecome older people."},{"time":414364,"text":"But if we could create sexuality education"},{"time":417823,"text":"that was more like pizza,"},{"time":420172,"text":"we could create education\nthat invites people"},{"time":423620,"text":"to think about their own desires,"},{"time":425915,"text":"to make deliberate decisions\nabout what they want,"},{"time":429167,"text":"to talk about it with their partners,"},{"time":431799,"text":"and to ultimately look for"},{"time":433472,"text":"not some external outcome"},{"time":436616,"text":"but for what feels satisfying,"},{"time":439773,"text":"and we get to decide that."},{"time":442292,"text":"You may have noticed"},{"time":443053,"text":"in the baseball and pizza comparison,"},{"time":445932,"text":"under the baseball, it's all commands."},{"time":448772,"text":"They're all exclamation points."},{"time":450869,"text":"But under the pizza\nmodel, they're questions."},{"time":453938,"text":"And who gets to answer those questions?"},{"time":455820,"text":"You do. I do."},{"time":459480,"text":"So remember, when we're thinking about"},{"time":461380,"text":"sexuality education and sexual activity,"},{"time":464126,"text":"baseball, you're out."},{"time":466316,"text":"Pizza is the way to think about healthy,"},{"time":469548,"text":"satisfying sexual activity,"},{"time":471988,"text":"and good, comprehensive\nsexuality education."},{"time":474928,"text":"Thank you very much for your time."},{"time":477158,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}